  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Digivolve][Veemon]: Cost 2 (When this Digimon would be
    deleted, you may trash the top card of this Digimon to prevent that deletion.)
    [When Digivolving] 1 of your opponent''s Digimon gets -2000 DP for the turn.
    If you have a blue or yellow Tamer in play, or if you have a card with the [Armor
    Form] trait in your trash, 1 of your opponent''s Digimon with 6000 DP or less
    can''t attack or block until the end of your opponent''s turn.'
